# hacker hive

## the idea

the hacker hive is a [[initiative|init]] to make prototype [housing](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Northside,_Berkeley,_California) [cooperatives](http://www.bsc.coop/) started by the [UC Berkeley hacker community](http://hackersatberkeley.com/).

some of us hackers already live together and some of us already work together. we invite all hackers to [[live]] and [[work]] together as the hacker hive, making a larger community with added [[benefits]] while retaining our own sub-hives of mates, friends, and family (see [[decentralization]]).

